name: Fast Frog Life
description:
A game made for the Mini Jam 106: Frogs².
Play as a Frog throughout its full life and try to reach your frog love in time before you turn into a old and senile grandpa frog.

W,A,S,D -> Move around
SPACE-> Swim Up / Jump
SHIFT -> Swim Down

Credits :
Skybox by Key Mouse
LowPolyTextures By N-hance Studio
